    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving naturally aspirated unit utilizes six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels through an M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed with a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a VANOS system refresh to ensure structural integrity and timing precision. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain exceptionally sharp.",
      "price": 31500.0,
