      "description": "Offering a meticulously maintained vehicle that perfectly balances performance with daily reliability. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and smoke-free. The premium leather upholstery is in excellent shape, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. All interior electronics, including the navigation system, heated seats, and sunroof, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in top form; the engine is quiet and responsive, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It has been serviced exclusively at authorized centers, with a comprehensive multi-point inspection and oil service completed within the last month. The tires have approximately 75% tread remaining, ensuring you won't need replacements anytime soon. This car represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, high-quality vehicle without the new-car price tag.",
